=== 與田寮村械鬥 ===
木橋頭村與鄰近的田寮村因風水、鄉村基建問題積怨多年。1937年，兩村因祖堂物業業權問題鬥上法庭。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Chinese Lineage and Society: Fukien and Kwantung Volume 33|last=Maurice Freedman|year=2021}}</ref>1960 年，兩村發生一場集體械鬥，雙方約百名村民攜帶鋤頭、鐵枝、木棍等作武器混戰，十多人受傷、三人重傷。約一小時後大批警員到場鎮壓，穿山甲隊留守兩村維持秩序。<ref>{{Cite web |date=1960-03-16 |title=新界元朗十八鄉之田寮村與木橋頭村 兩村大鬥悲劇 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFCadagDU5dtu&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=1&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc |website= |publisher=華僑日報}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=1960-03-17 |title=田寮木橋頭兩村械鬥 獲致和平解決 簽署保證書今後不再發生同類事件 |url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E6%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E9%A0%AD%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FH7zGe%2FKF%2BFG15vTKXfFiv&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=2&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc |publisher=華僑日報}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=